    "actor_description": "The breath leaves me all at once, like my body finally got the message. My shoulders unclench. The tight band around my ribs loosens. For a second I just stand there and let the “not happening” of it sink in.",
    "description_text": "{actor} lets out a long, audible exhale. Their shoulders drop; their face softens from braced to human again. Whatever they were holding in their posture drains out in one slow release.",
